Serge Nadaud https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serge_Nadaud 0 Serge Nadaud (May 14, 1906 – July 18, 1995) was a Russian-born French stage and film actor. He was born Eugene Rabinowitch to a Jewish family in Bakhmut which was then part of the Russian Empire. Sometime after the Russian Revolution of 1917 his family emigrated to France and settled there. He was a noted voice actor, dubbing foreign films for release in France. Serge_Nadaud ( May_14_,_1906 – July_18_,_1995 ) was a_Russian-born_French_stage_and_film_actor .
